description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Reporting to the Head of Workforce, the focus of this role will be to provide a professional HR Advisory service and work in partnership with directorates within the Integrated Care Strategic Business Unit (SBU) to drive forward high levels of performance, engagement and productivity in line with key workforce and organisational priorities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Acting as a key point of contact for managers within Integrated Care you will be solution focused and will use your initiative to pro-actively monitor workforce metrics to improve performance and to resolve any workforce issues in a timely and accurate manner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will lead and support the implementation of change management programmes, as well as leading on staff engagement projects, such as the national staff survey and more bespoke areas of focus. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role is varied and you will lead a number of projects to support recruitment, retention and equality, diversity and inclusion plans as well as supporting directorates with the workforce planning element of the annual business planning cycle. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Within Integrated Care we have a commitment to providing an inclusive workplace for all our staff and we are seeking talented staff to build a diverse workforce which accurately reflects the patients and population that we serve.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will be a CIPD qualified workforce professional who is passionate about supporting our people within Integrated Care. You will possess excellent communication skills, with the ability to inspire trust and confidence in your advice. Attention to detail, good analytical skills and a strong sense of customer focus is essential for the role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Should you wish to discuss the position, please contact Fran Talbot, Head of Workforce – Integrated Care on &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;frances.talbot@gstt.nhs.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameFran TalbotJob titleHead of WorkforceEmail addressfrances.talbot@gstt.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
